{"tid":1057843,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"港女陳靜有份演《Marvel隊長》？","createTime":"2019-03-12T07:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T14:54:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"df0c1acb2f281116121ca97ff8cf2e3c1588ca11","tid":1057843,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"《Marvel隊長》喺上個星期上畫，香港票房大收三千萬，直逼《神奇女俠》。戲中焦點除左貓仔Goose之外，飾演Kree族狙擊手Minn-Eva的陳靜（Gemma Chan）一樣咁搶眼，原來佢係香港人後代！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2019/03/Minn-Eva3_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2019%2F03%2FMinn-Eva3_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg&h=0ba0c26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然戲份唔多，但都算係唔錯架喇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信有留意開西片觀眾都唔會對Gemma陌生，因為佢舊年有份主演《我的超豪男友》飾演堅毅名媛Astrid大受關注，早前佢一身桃紅色晚裝現身奧斯卡頒奬禮吸引唔少媒體。Gemma以前曾經演出過《怪獸與牠們的產地》、《變形金剛5》等電影，喺BBC劇集《新福爾摩斯》曾經做過其中一集嘅主演。<br />\n<br />\nGemma喺倫敦出世，爸爸係香港人，媽媽好彩喺文革移民左去英國，佢喺比較傳統嘅華人家庭長大，自小就學芭蕾舞、鋼琴、小提琴。佢都順應屋企人要求考入牛津法系，但係心裏面嘅最大夢想始終都係成為演員。Gemma大學畢業之後唔去做律師樓實習，而係成為兼職model賺錢讀戲劇學校，之後喺參加左一套英國真人騷《Project Catwalk》而被英國電影製片人發掘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2019/03/gemma_chan_06042017_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2019%2F03%2Fgemma_chan_06042017_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg&h=dbcd5315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然華裔演員好難得可以喺荷里活有演出機會，但係Gemma唔會亂咁接戲拍，有傳2012嘅《新鐵金剛：智破天凶城》本來由係由佢做邦女郎，但佢最後放棄左難得機會，因為佢認為戲中嘅祼露頭係冇必要。今時今日亞洲演員開始喺歐美影壇多左演出機會，相信Gemma可以有繼續有更好發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/article/361826-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD%E6%BC%94%E3%80%8Amarvel%E9%9A%8A%E9%95%B7%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%9F-%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A%E6%89%8Bminn-eva%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E6%8F%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Farticle%2F361826-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E6%25BC%2594%25E3%2580%258Amarvel%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E3%2580%258B%25EF%25BC%259F-%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2589%258Bminn-eva%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E6%258F%25AD&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6NUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=fb20f6d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upower.com.hk/article/361826-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD%E6%BC%94%E3%80%8Amarvel%E9%9A%8A%E9%95%B7%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%9F-%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A%E6%89%8Bminn-eva%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E6%8F%AD</a>"},{"pid":"63389eb9308d94283cc300277a7d7c13718abfad","tid":1057843,"uid":59920,"like":4,"dislike":84,"score":-80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"DADA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6978719c3975560a3c3c3b574de0b682f05ba0fc","tid":1057843,"uid":130198,"like":1,"dislike":46,"score":-45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"最尾見到有個中國人 但上網搵完都唔知邊個黎"},{"pid":"697de0b5c2fef4bf8fd89a9056237d85d017994d","tid":1057843,"uid":34123,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe9976047bc683667fd28e6271c2fbc15d848db","tid":1057843,"uid":2419,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3d760c69b3aba3f8c7caeed7396c227ddacd5e","tid":105784